  "3304080": {
    "name": "DrillScape",
    "steam_appid": 3304080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/869109e4385e4bbbb9fd6ec304ec1719.webp?t=1770920957\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你操控一辆高速探测车，在被感染的星球上进行探索。挖掘外星地形、对抗敌对生物、提取资源，并在能量耗尽前返回基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次任务都会让你深入不断蔓延的外星感染区域。风险越大，收益越多，但停留过久可能会失去一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/dadfc4ca4010f448c763f5d476e44e06.poster.avif?t=1770920957\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/dadfc4ca4010f448c763f5d476e44e06.webm?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/dadfc4ca4010f448c763f5d476e44e06.mp4?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌对生物从星球本身涌现。战斗节奏快速，迫使你不断对周围环境做出反应。感染蔓延得越深，每颗星球就变得越危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/cbd6f8e8b9716c7c6dd465dbecb1bd80.poster.avif?t=1770920957\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/cbd6f8e8b9716c7c6dd465dbecb1bd80.webm?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/cbd6f8e8b9716c7c6dd465dbecb1bd80.mp4?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每颗星球都由一个中心核心控制。找到它意味着要穿过更坚硬的地形和更强大的敌人。移除核心可以阻止感染，但会触发星球居民的激烈反应。你的决定决定了感染如何在全球蔓延。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/2be9e46e86ad1513efed9a68c66467f0.poster.avif?t=1770920957\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/2be9e46e86ad1513efed9a68c66467f0.webm?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/2be9e46e86ad1513efed9a68c66467f0.mp4?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开采不同的矿石来推动进度。资源有限。你必须决定何时深入挖掘，何时在能量耗尽或失去一切之前返回基地。风险与回报始终处于平衡中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/ffeda15246e0b4296948da9c8f7e5611.poster.avif?t=1770920957\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/ffeda15246e0b4296948da9c8f7e5611.webm?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304080/extras/ffeda15246e0b4296948da9c8f7e5611.mp4?t=1770920957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用提取的资源升级你的探测车。改进武器、能力和能量管理，以适应你的游戏风格。每次任务都能尝试新的配置和策略，为更危险的星球和更深层次的感染做准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>特性</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以采矿和探索为核心的动作类Roguelike游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的星球，感染等级不断提升</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于能量的风险系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模块化升级和多样化构建</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感染在星球间蔓延的动态全球地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高对比度视觉设计的2D像素艺术</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
